The paper discusses the problem of deploying service function chains over a network function virtualized architecture, which is a topic related to computer networks and distributed systems (cs.NI, cs.DC). The paper also presents an optimization problem and proposes a heuristic approach to solve it, which falls under the category of operations research and optimization (cs.SY). The paper uses statistical analysis to model link and server queues, which is related to data science (cs.DS). Finally, the paper proposes an affinity-based approach to solve the problem, which involves machine learning techniques (cs.AI).
